{"tid":2322684,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"高等法院後勤支援員工初步確診","createTime":"2020-12-12T13:27:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T15:30:05.000Z","uid":240362,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9bfa981b3555398993fa55d1e91c10b2b6960b40","tid":2322684,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:27:39.000Z","msg":"司法機構後勤支援員工初步確診2019冠狀病毒病<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n下稿代司法機構發出︰<br />\n<br />\n  司法機構今日（十二月十二日）表示，一名負責後勤支援工作的員工今日初步確診2019冠狀病毒病。<br />\n<br />\n  有關員工於高等法院大樓工作，該員工的工作並不需要接觸法庭使用者。該員工於星期四（十二月十日）感到不適，並於今日初步確診。<br />\n<br />\n  為慎重起見，司法機構已立即安排清潔和消毒法院大樓內相關法庭、辦公室和公眾地方，有關清潔工作已經完成，沒有影響法院大樓運作，法院大樓亦會於星期一（十二月十四日）如常開放。<br />\n<br />\n  司法機構目前並無接獲衞生防護中心通知，有任何司法機構員工或其他人士被列為該員工的密切接觸者。<br />\n<br />\n  為向公眾提供進一步資訊，有關過去十四日涉及曾在法院大樓工作的員工，以及在法院範圍逗留較長時間的法庭使用者的確診／初步確診個案，已上載於司法機構網頁（<a href=\"http://www.judiciary.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.judiciary.hk&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcqZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=eed8959f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.judiciary.hk</a>），以供查閱。<br />\n<br />\n  司法機構會繼續嚴格實施適當的預防及人流管理措施，包括加強清潔和消毒公用地方，要求所有進入法院大樓的人士接受體溫檢測，除非法官另有指示，須時刻佩戴口罩，以及實施適當的管理措施以控制人流和避免人群聚集。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年12月12日（星期六）<br />\n香港時間21時05分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202012/12/P2020121200708.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202012%2F12%2FP2020121200708.htm&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcqZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=4fd2d571\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202012/12/P2020121200708.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9f50fad1ddf6bfb5a7d8256bf8f01b3612c2a3a3","tid":2322684,"uid":76804,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:28:05.000Z","msg":"希望全部都係dead body"},{"pid":"08c3f6158842049b11878c63e5fbe3f85f9e481b","tid":2322684,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be183b6c59425b0cca8fef18a0deb8ae621bd38e","tid":2322684,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:29:59.000Z","msg":"＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊"},{"pid":"5eb5e78e9b81a4352703183c581945ef636a4e52","tid":2322684,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:31:12.000Z","msg":"去過法院嗰邊聽審嘅手足要小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab517fd34b0e482ae75d72039207795fe05b87c4","tid":2322684,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:44:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ef650b7da3c947411dd6805b4989e4b01cd99a","tid":2322684,"uid":198181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae11b873625d9d7ae9286ce44aa520a363b2252","tid":2322684,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2c81b4ecf734805d3e8f4f3b6bf71c1e104111